        "title": "DevOps Engineer (m/f/x) | Cloud | Azure | C# | Computer Science",
        "description": "<p>Thrive on innovation at a global technology leader. Develop exciting solutions in a diverse, stable work environment that's focused on the future. Join us in a modern work environment with an open and inspiring culture and colleagues!</p>\n<h2>A job to get excited about!</h2>\n<p>Is \"state of the art\" a term that speaks to you? Why just watch as others shape the future when you could play an active role? At our company, you are part of the action in the development of cloud infrastructure. Your challenges:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>to increase Azure DevOps automation by developing and modifying tools and scripts </li>\n<li>to design, maintain and oversee build and release pipelines</li>\n<li>to analyze new tools and technologies for future use in software development</li>\n<li>to administer physical servers now and cloud servers in the future</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Your talents</h2>\n<p>Have we piqued your interest? Are you someone who seizes the initiative and prefers celebrating successes as a member of a team?</p>\n<ul>\n<li>a degree in computer science or a similar qualification</li>\n<li>ideally, professional experience in a relevant field - but we are happy to give recent graduates a chance</li>\n<li>knowledge of object-oriented programming languages like C# or PowerShell are beneficial</li>\n<li>a good command of written and spoken German and English</li>\n</ul>\n<p>At ZEISS we encourage creative thinking and innovation. We work in dynamic and interdisciplinary teams and offer individual development perspectives as well as flexibility in organizing your work. We care about our employees and take particular responsibility for improving society and preserving our environment. These core values have shaped our corporate culture at ZEISS for over 170 years.</p>\n<h2>Help us shape the future!</h2>\n<p>The application process takes less than 10 minutes, we look forward to receiving your application via the application form!</p>\n<h2>Your contact</h2>\n<p>Carl Zeiss Industrielle Messtechnik GmbH</p>\n<p>Miriam Fuchs</p>\n<p>+497364209149</p>\n",
