        "title": "Senior Data Engineer, Data Platform",
        "description": "<p>We’re looking for a Senior Infrastructure Engineer to join our Data Platform team to help us build great infrastructure and tooling for data scientists, engineers as well as product, marketing and business experts. Our Data Platform Team is responsible for building and running the systems that allow us to store, manage and expose our data in order to make rapid data informed decisions and engaging experiences for our users.</p>\n<p>As a Senior Data Engineer, you will be empowering our Engineers to securely and effortlessly manage, process and consume data. You’ll help maintain and improve our event pipeline, job scheduler, monitoring, storage, queuing and query systems based on Kafka, HDFS, Cassandra, S3/GCS, Spark, Airflow and BigQuery.</p>\n<p>You are an experienced Software Engineer or Systems Engineer with a track record of simplifying efficient, scalable and accessible systems, preferably in the domain of databases, data infrastructure and tooling. You are passionate about educating others to efficiently build data pipelines, with a solid background in Java, Scala, Python and SQL. Your empathy for your users' goals, enthusiasm working across teams and desire to impact the world of music and creative expression are ingredients for your success.</p>\n<p>Read more about SoundCloud Engineering <a href=\"https://developers.soundcloud.com/blog/engineering-levels\">here</a></p>\n<p><strong>Diversity at SoundCloud</strong></p>\n<p><em>SoundCloud is for everyone. Diversity and open expression are fundamental to our organization; they help us build a social platform and global community where anyone can create, discover, and share sounds. We acknowledge the challenges in our industry, and strive to develop an inclusive culture where everyone can contribute.</em></p>\n",
        "how_to_apply": "<p>Apply via this link: <a href=\"https://jobs.soundcloud.com/job?gh_jid=4255588002\">https://jobs.soundcloud.com/job?gh_jid=4255588002</a> or email your CV to <a href=\"mailto:anya.voronova@soundcloud.com\">anya.voronova@soundcloud.com</a></p>\n",
