        "location": "Berlin",
        "title": "Mobile C Developer",
        "description": "<p>Adjust is a fast-growing mobile marketing analytics company. We build business intelligence for mobile apps, placing a high premium on scientific statistics, hand-in-glove UX, and lean, pragmatic product iteration. We enable marketers to understand how their marketing campaigns are performing.</p>\n<p><strong>Your Role:</strong></p>\n<p>As part of our Fraud Squad, you will conduct research and develop solutions based on the latest security trends to protect the integrity of Adjust’s products as well as in-depth security assessments on mobile apps and our open-source solutions. Furthermore, you will participate in code review sessions for the other team members’ work and contribute in streamlining the delivery of the security solutions to mobile infrastructures.</p>\n<p><strong>Your tasks:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Research, prototype and implement solutions to enhance the integrity and security of Adjust’s proprietary products</li>\n<li>Develop, automate and maintain Adjust’s current proprietary security solutions</li>\n<li>Conduct blackbox testing on Adjust’s solutions and in-depth security assessments on mobile apps</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Your Profile:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Experience in software development, security, and/or system administration</li>\n<li>Good understanding of C and UNIX toolset</li>\n<li>Experience in at least one scripting languages e.g. Bash</li>\n<li>Understanding of Android/iOS internals and first experience in penetration testing, secure coding, reverse engineering or forensics is a plus</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>What we offer you:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>A competitive salary</li>\n<li>Flexibility in work schedule</li>\n<li>Relocation assistance</li>\n<li>An international team with strong focus on transparency</li>\n<li>Regular team gatherings and company retreats</li>\n<li>An opportunity to do office exchanges in other satellite locations</li>\n<li>Additional perks such as Friday team lunches and free access to our company gym</li>\n</ul>\n<p>More details about our company culture and perks can be found on our careers page.</p>\n<p><strong>Interested? Let’s Talk! Please apply right here !</strong></p>\n",
