        "location": "New York, NY",
        "title": "Full Stack DevOps Engineer",
        "description": "<p>Are you a gamer who also loves working on innovative technologies as much as we do? Want to create the next generation of gaming world? Come, join us!</p>\n<p>Anzu is a fast-growing startup on a mission to bring real-world brand ads to video gaming and eSports. We are at the forefront of in-game advertising driven by an ambitious team, with offices in Tel Aviv and Berlin. In a short time since incorporation, we have made our presence felt in the industry, winning awards such as the VideoTrends 2018 awards, SPROCKIT Best Monetization Company 2019, VivaTech Orange Lab 2019 and a number of others. We work with top names in gaming, eSports and advertising world - PepsiCo, Turner, Rocket League.</p>\n<p>WHAT’S IN IT FOR YOU?</p>\n<p>*Opportunity to lead the automation, deployment and monitoring development at Anzu</p>\n<p>*Work on Anzu’s automation infrastructure for handling all the back-end services logic and running E2E tests</p>\n<p>*Work on real-time event sourcing infrastructure</p>\n<p>*Work on monitoring infrastructure for real-time scaling and error detection</p>\n<p>*Work on deployment infrastructure for automatic deployments, automatic failover handling</p>\n<p>*Be open to learning new technologies and applying them in your day-to-day tasks</p>\n<p>WHAT DO YOU NEED TO BE PART OF ANZU?</p>\n<p>*Backend technologies (at least 3 to qualify), 2 yrs experience:</p>\n<pre><code>  Intermediate Node.js knowledge \n  Intermediate Databases knowledge \n             Both noSQL &amp; relational\n  Intermediate Bash / PowerShell knowledge\n  Docker &amp; kubernetes\n  Cloud networking, architectures &amp; deployments\n  Cicd systems\n  Centralised monitoring &amp; logging (Prometheus / Grafana)\n</code></pre>\n<p>*Front technologies, 2 yrs experience - big advantage:</p>\n<pre><code>   HTML5 \n   CSS3\n   Vanilla Javascript, React\n   Webpack, NPM\n   Browser API's\n</code></pre>\n<p>*Prior collaboration with a well-known advertising or game development company - big advantage</p>\n",
        "how_to_apply": "<p>Interested? Email CV to <a href=\"mailto:natalia@anzu.io\">natalia@anzu.io</a></p>\n",
